headline: Billionaire Bill Gates' Foundation Bought Just 2 Stocks in Q3, and It's Bullish for This Sector
summary: Bill Gates is one of the most famous businessmen in the world.  The Microsoft founder is still one of the richest people in the world, and the foundation's portfolio reflects that as it has more than $45 billion in assets under management.
